23. Qg3+ $3 {A key move, that wins}) 20... Kc7 21. Qf4+ Kb6 22. Qee3+ $2 {A
very natural, human move, but it would appear that this move jeopardizes the
win} (22. Bd3 $1 {Was the strongest. Black obviously can't capture the bishop.}
Qb3 23. Qee3+ d4 24. Qfxd4+ Nxd4+ 25. Qxd4+ Kc7 26. g8=Q {And wins} Qxg8 27.
Qc3+ Kd6 28. Rh6+) 22... Bc5 23. g8=Q b1=Q {[pgndiagram] A remarkable picture.
